'''鎝(V)酸鈉'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，[[化学式|化学式]]为NaTcO<sub>3</sub>，是一种[[钙钛矿_(结构)|钙钛矿]]材料。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Materials Chemistry C|volume=4|issue=15|language=en|issn=2050-7526|date=2016|pages=3157–3167|doi=10.1039/C5TC04172D|url=http://xlink.rsc.org/?DOI=C5TC04172D|title=Stability and electronic properties of new inorganic perovskites from high-throughput ab initio calculations|accessdate=2019-02-24|author=Sabine Körbel, Miguel A. L. Marques, Silvana Botti}}</ref>它可由[[锝|锝]]、[[高锝酸钠|高锝酸钠]]和[[氧化钠|氧化钠]]共热制得，高温下发生歧化。<ref>无机化学丛书. 第九卷 锰分族 铁系 铂系. pp 122. 3.11 氧化数为V的锝和铼化合物</ref>此外，Na<sub>2</sub><sup>99</sup>MoO<sub>4</sub>在NaOH溶液的[[放射性衰變|衰变]]也会产生NaTcO<sub>3</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=The International Journal of Applied Radiation and Isotopes|volume=36|issue=3|language=en|date=1985-3|pages=219–222|doi=10.1016/0020-708X(85)90071-7|url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/0020708X85900717|title=Determination of 99mTc valent form in solids by measurement of internal conversion electrons|accessdate=2019-02-24|author=M. Fis̆er, V. Brabec, O. Dragoun, A. Kovalík, J. Frána, M. Rys̆avý}}</ref>NaTcO<sub>3</sub>的puckering效应比NaMoO<sub>3</sub>小，e<sub>g</sub><sup>π</sup>和a<sub>1g</sub>态间带消失。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Materials Chemistry A|volume=6|issue=8|language=en|issn=2050-7488|date=2018|pages=3747–3753|doi=10.1039/C7TA10826E|url=http://xlink.rsc.org/?DOI=C7TA10826E|title=Oxygen redox in hexagonal layered Na x TMO 3 (TM = 4d elements) for high capacity Na ion batteries|accessdate=2019-02-24|author=M. H. N. Assadi, Masashi Okubo, Atsuo Yamada, Yoshitaka Tateyama}}</ref>

